        public Booking(int id,
               java.lang.String passengerName,
               java.lang.String location,
               java.lang.String destination,
               java.lang.String airplaneName,
               double cost,
               int seatNo,
               SeatType seatType,
               java.util.Map<FoodItem,java.lang.Integer> foodMap)
        Constructs a Booking object using the provided parameters
        Parameters:
        id - the ID of the booking.
        passengerName - the name of the booking's corresponding passenger.
        location - the location from where the booking's corresponding flight starts.
        destination - the destination of the booking's corresponding flight.
        airplaneName - the name of the booking's corresponding airplane.
        cost - the cost of the booking.
        seatNo - the seat number for the booking.
        seatType - the seat type of the booking. Can be either ECONOMY_SEAT or BUSINESS_SEAT.
        foodMap - a map between the ordered food items and the ordered quantity of each item.
